room_title: Escape room "Pirate Adventure" by Inland Empire Escape Rooms in Riverside

You and your team find yourself suddenly imprisoned in the notorious Captain Morganâ€™s Cove! With only a small window of opportunity to escape before your captors return, can you find your way to the beach and the promise of freedom?
